{"title":"只因为","authors":["杜运燮"],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":5,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"只因为"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杜运燮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你身旁有阴影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只因为你自己"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挡住了阳光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能把阴影甩到背后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只因为你没有"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝着太阳的方向走"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看耀眼的阳光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仍然是一片灰暗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只因眼睛刚睁开"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看不清好景色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切是一样的模糊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只因眼泪未擦干"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你听不见墙外"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火车高速奔跑声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只因你关了门窗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的琴再不象往日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弹不出高昂的曲调"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只因没绷紧琴弦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的歌没有人爱唱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只因为象衰老的秋草"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拨不动那千万根心弦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在大道上也跑不快"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只因你跑的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总是向后扭着头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的视野总觉得窄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只因你在河床里流动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还没有投进大海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作品太浅，没阳光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只因你转来转去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总在生活的边沿"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}